# ITC_Coq: Formal Proofs of Indirect Treatment Comparisons
#
# This project formalizes propensity score theory, doubly robust estimation,
# and MAIC vs STC comparison using measure-theoretic foundations.
#
# Dependencies:
#   coq-mathcomp-ssreflect >= 2.0
#   coq-mathcomp-algebra
#   coq-mathcomp-analysis >= 1.9.0
#   coq-hierarchy-builder >= 1.6.0

-R theories ITC

# Phase 1: Foundations
theories/Axioms.v
theories/BasicTypes.v
theories/PotentialOutcomes.v
theories/CausalAssumptions.v

# Phase 2: Core Theory
theories/ConditionalIndep.v
theories/BalancingScore.v
theories/PropensityScore.v

# Phase 3: Estimators
theories/IPWEstimator.v
theories/OutcomeRegression.v
theories/DoublyRobust.v

# Phase 4: ITC Methods
theories/MAIC.v
theories/STC.v
theories/Comparison.v
